（中間：入遊戲開始打歌）<br />\n（右邊： 遊戲設定 同 耳機音量）<br />\n<br />\n去左邊然後撳招募<br />\n<br />\n另一邊嘅朋友  係未選擇歌曲嘅情況下<br />\n就會收到一個邀請（即使你哋網頁未加friend）<br />\n另一邊嘅朋友就要去一個 area<br />\n喺new song嘅左手邊<br />\n即是<br />\n（目標邀約）（New Song）(Bonus Area)（排位）<br />\n<br />\n朋友去嗰個藍色嘅地方 目標邀約位<br />\n入去就可以進行聯機啦<br />\n<br />\n注意事項！！！！<br />\n如果樓主只有三個人玩<br />\n咁第三位仁兄就只可以同你地打三首歌<br />\n如果想大家一齊打曬四首歌<br />\n唯一方法就係四個人遊玩<br />\n<br />\n三個人想一齊打曬四首歌嘅方法<br />\n就係第三條友盡快入錢重新入game<br />\n再加入你哋<br />\n但第一set嘅朋友就必須要慢慢嚟<br />\n等埋佢入game<br />\n<br />\n我知我講得甩甩咳咳 sor ar<br />\n有咩唔明再問啦"},{"pid":"8b20a542b49ac3841cb7c6f4d63c0e399e8f3128","tid":2091394,"uid":225168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"4連咪就係track start個畫面最左邊藍色格仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n部機都黎左成半年都唔知 Siu4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9a6161cd1b75b12fb5f478401a21ef25d17345","tid":2091394,"uid":360663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aa68d3808f6a0064f6220a06f61b28862147902","tid":2091394,"uid":219050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"我有個fd係高手😂可以約<br />\n利申新手)想揾fd"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"我都係"},{"pid":"bfe336eeb71f8af7f3a816863d9ed3f843921526","tid":2091394,"uid":360663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b20a542b49ac3841cb7c6